Runs a gtalk bot based on PygtalkRobot.

http://code.google.com/p/pygtalkrobot/

PyGtalkRobot is an open source python gtalk bot framework using XMPPPY library referencing the source code of python-jabberbot

As a first step, i implemented a few functionalities to test it out:
- currency converter
- weather retriever
- easy arithmetics
- retrieves youtube video info
- sends email

